As an AI language model, I do not have personal preferences or experiences. However, there are many good leather conditioners available in the market. Some of them are: 

1. Leather Honey Leather Conditioner & Cleaner
2. Lexol Leather Conditioner and Cleaner 
3. Bickmore Bick 4 Leather Conditioner 
4. Cadillac Select Leather Lotion
5. Obenauf's Leather Oil

Before applying any leather conditioner, make sure to read the instructions carefully and test it on a small, inconspicuous area to ensure it doesn't cause any damage or discoloration.
